{
  "id": "adv_event_2201_01_01",
  "title": "恩返しの\nサプライズ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "おまたせ～！\nみんなで集まって何話してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry I’m late!\nWhat were you all talking about together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.3654876709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、さくら\n年末年始は忙しくて休む暇もないわねって話してたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Sakura.\nWe were saying the New Year period is so busy we have no time to rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.558820947,
      "endTime": 13.3828573545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "大晦日はカウントダウンライブに出演……\n元旦はテレビの生放送で新年初ライブ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Countdown live show on New Year’s Eve…\nBroadcast live on New Year’s Day…for the first job…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5828575452,
      "endTime": 22.2699100811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "毎年話題のカウントダウンライブに\n出演出来るなんて夢みたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s like a dream that we can appear\non the countdown live show that everyone talks about each year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4832432429,
      "endTime": 28.176327292099998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "人気アーティストが大勢参加する大きなイベントだから\n気を引き締めないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a big event with a crowd of popular artists joining in‚\nso we have to stay focus.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3763274828,
      "endTime": 34.1423590341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "今年一年の集大成にふさわしい舞台……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The right stage for the culmination of this whole year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3423589388,
      "endTime": 38.5076877276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "一年の集大成か……\n今年はいろんなことがあったよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The culmination of the year…\nA lot of things happened this year…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.72102108,
      "endTime": 43.8250572204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんが星見プロに入社したのも今年だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Satomi-san joining Hoshimi Productions was this year too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2666666667,
      "endTime": 49.1307936351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "すっかり馴染んでるから忘れがちだけど\nさとみさんってまだ入社一年目の新人なのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re so used to her that it’s easy to forget‚\nbut Satomi-san is still new‚ in her first year in the company.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3,
      "endTime": 56.1511965336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "今では星見プロに欠かせない縁の下の力持ちだわ\n仕事熱心で、タレントを大事にしてくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now she’s the unsung hero in Hoshimi Productions.\nShe’s passionate about her job and cares about the idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3333333333,
      "endTime": 64.7664631367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "何人も掛け持ちで大変なのに\nいつも元気一杯で現場に来てくれるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s tough for her to take care of so many people at once‚\nbut she always comes to work full of energy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9666666667,
      "endTime": 70.81619108529999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのって凄く心強いよね\nこの間なんて同時刻に二つの現場に現れたらしいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s really reassuring.\nThe other day she seems to have been in two places at the same time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0333333333,
      "endTime": 80.4842411519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "分身の術……？　短時間で複数の現場を行き来する……\nさとみさんの移動手段、謎……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shadow Clone Jutsu? Going to multiple places in a short time?\nSatomi-san's move….mystery…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6666666667,
      "endTime": 89.9627674263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "彼女のバイタリティとフットワークの軽さは\n私達も見習わないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’d do well to learn from her\nvitality and light footwork.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1666666667,
      "endTime": 95.423272864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "今年の重大ニュースといえば……\nリズノワとトリエルの電撃移籍……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For another big news this year…\nThe lightning transfers of LizNoir and TRINITYAiLE…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1333333333,
      "endTime": 101.9987975746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "びっくりしたよね\nまさかあの二グループが星見プロに入るなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised.\nI couldn’t believe those two groups would join Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2,
      "endTime": 107.989868608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達からは学ぶことが沢山あるわ\n莉央さんや瑠依のストイックさは私も見習わないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have a lot to learn from those girls.\nI need to learn from Rio-san and Rui’s strictness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2,
      "endTime": 117.02881470710001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんも十分ストイックだと思うけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you’re strict with yourself enough‚ Rei-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2333333333,
      "endTime": 121.0878684838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで合宿して新曲を作ったのも今年だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was this year that we all had our camp to write the new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3,
      "endTime": 125.1812926292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "大変だったけど、みんなでお料理をしたり\nホラー映画を観たりして楽しかったなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was tough‚ but it was fun too‚\ncooking together‚ watching horror movies and stuff…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3666666667,
      "endTime": 132.51919296469998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "今年は一人一人が飛躍した年でもあったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This was a year when each of us made a lot of progress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7333333333,
      "endTime": 136.5389116128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "千紗の単独グラビアや雫のラジオ出演も評判が良くて\nみんなアイドルとして成長したわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa’s solo photoshoot and Shizuku’s radio appearances were popular too.\nWe all grew as idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7333333333,
      "endTime": 144.57230841330002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんもバラエティ番組の仕事が増えた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve been getting more TV variety show jobs‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.7666666667,
      "endTime": 149.1624265353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "そこは不本意なんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although I didn’t intend that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3333333333,
      "endTime": 151.74215424850001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "今年一年いろいろあったね\n大晦日のライブはそんな一年の集大成なんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A lot of stuff happened this year.\nAnd the show on New Year’s Eve will be the culmination of this year…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.9666666667,
      "endTime": 160.49504220260002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "そのカウントダウンライブで……\nサニピの新曲をサプライズ発表する……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That countdown live will feature…\nthe surprise launch of the new Sunny Peace song….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.7,
      "endTime": 166.9415585085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "告知なしで新曲披露なんて、みんな驚くでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone will be amazed by the unannounced unveiling of a new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.1666666667,
      "endTime": 171.3259863536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんなへのサプライズプレゼント……\n喜んでもらえるといいな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A surprise present for all the fans.\nI hope they like it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.5333333333,
      "endTime": 178.03725482910002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
